<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>Deepdub QC — operator slots in use</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/app.css"></head>
<body>
<main class="centered-panel">
  <div class="panel">
    <div class="wordmark">▐DD▌ Deepdub QC</div>
    <h1>Both operator slots are in use</h1>
